{"id":107,"ayahs":[{"number":3,"arabic":"حُرِّمَتْ عَلَيْكُمُ ٱلْمَيْتَةُ وَٱلدَّمُ وَلَحْمُ ٱلْخِنزِيرِ وَمَآ أُهِلَّ لِغَيْرِ ٱللَّهِ بِهِۦ وَٱلْمُنْخَنِقَةُ وَٱلْمَوْقُوذَةُ وَٱلْمُتَرَدِّيَةُ وَٱلنَّطِيحَةُ وَمَآ أَكَلَ ٱلسَّبُعُ إِلَّا مَا ذَكَّيْتُمْ وَمَا ذُبِحَ عَلَى ٱلنُّصُبِ وَأَن تَسْتَقْسِمُوا۟ بِٱلْأَزْلَٰمِ ۚ ذَٰلِكُمْ فِسْقٌ ۗ ٱلْيَوْمَ يَئِسَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ مِن دِينِكُمْ فَلَا تَخْشَوْهُمْ وَٱخْشَوْنِ ۚ ٱلْيَوْمَ أَكْمَلْتُ لَكُمْ دِينَكُمْ وَأَتْمَمْتُ عَلَيْكُمْ نِعْمَتِى وَرَضِيتُ لَكُمُ ٱلْإِسْلَٰمَ دِينًۭا ۚ فَمَنِ ٱضْطُرَّ فِى مَخْمَصَةٍ غَيْرَ مُتَجَانِفٍۢ لِّإِثْمٍۢ ۙ فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ غَفُورٌۭ رَّحِيمٌۭ","translation":"FORBIDDEN to you is carrion, and blood, and the flesh of swine, and that over which any name other than God's has been invoked, and the animal that has been strangled, or beaten to death, or killed by a fall, or gored to death, or savaged by a beast of prey, save that which you [yourselves] may have slaughtered while it was still alive; and [forbidden to you is] all that has been slaughtered on idolatrous altars. And [you are forbidden] to seek to learn through divination what the future may hold in store for you: this is sinful conduct. Today, those who are bent on denying the truth have lost all hope of [your ever forsaking] your religion: do not, then, hold them in awe, but stand in awe of Me! Today have I perfected your religious law for you, and have bestowed upon you the full measure of My blessings, and willed that self-surrender unto Me shall be your religion. As for him, however, who is driven [to what is forbidden] by dire necessity and not by an inclination to sinning -behold, God is much-forgiving, a dispenser of grace.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/672.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":2645,"position":1,"arabic":"حُرِّمَتْ","translation":"অবৈধ করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2646,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمُ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2647,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَيْتَةُ","translation":"মৃত (পশু পাখী)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2648,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلدَّمُ","translation":"ও (প্রবাহিত) রক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2649,"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَحْمُ","translation":"ও গোশত","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2650,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْخِنزِيرِ","translation":"শুকরের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2651,"position":7,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"ও যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2652,"position":8,"arabic":"أُهِلَّ","translation":"জবাই করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2653,"position":9,"arabic":"لِغَيْرِ","translation":"(জন্যে নয়) ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2654,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর (নামে)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2655,"position":11,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2656,"position":12,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُنْخَنِقَةُ","translation":"ও শ্বাসরোধে মৃত জন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2657,"position":13,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَوْقُوذَةُ","translation":"ও আঘাতে মৃত জন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2658,"position":14,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُتَرَدِّيَةُ","translation":"ও উপর থেকে পড়ে মৃত জন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2659,"position":15,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّطِيحَةُ","translation":"ও শিঙের আঘাতে মৃত (পশু)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2660,"position":16,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"ও যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2661,"position":17,"arabic":"أَكَلَ","translation":"খেয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2662,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلسَّبُعُ","translation":"হিংস্র পশুতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2663,"position":19,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2664,"position":20,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2665,"position":21,"arabic":"ذَكَّيْتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা (জবাই করে) পবিত্র করেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2666,"position":22,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং (হারাম) যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2667,"position":23,"arabic":"ذُبِحَ","translation":"বলি দেয়া হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2668,"position":24,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2669,"position":25,"arabic":"ٱلنُّصُبِ","translation":"পূজার বেদীসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2670,"position":26,"arabic":"وَأَن","translation":"এবং (এও হারাম) যে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2671,"position":27,"arabic":"تَسْتَقْسِمُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা ভাগ্য নির্ণয় করো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2672,"position":28,"arabic":"بِٱلْأَزْلَـٰمِ ۚ","translation":"দিয়ে জুয়ার তীরগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2674,"position":29,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكُمْ","translation":"এসব","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2675,"position":30,"arabic":"فِسْقٌ ۗ","translation":"পাপকাজ  (কাজ)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2677,"position":31,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ","translation":"আজ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2678,"position":32,"arabic":"يَئِسَ","translation":"নিরাশ হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2679,"position":33,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2680,"position":34,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অবিশ্বাস করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2681,"position":35,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2682,"position":36,"arabic":"دِينِكُمْ","translation":"দীন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2683,"position":37,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"অতএব না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2684,"position":38,"arabic":"تَخْشَوْهُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ভয় কর তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2685,"position":39,"arabic":"وَٱخْشَوْنِ ۚ","translation":"এবং তোমরা ভয় কর আমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2687,"position":40,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ","translation":"আজ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2688,"position":41,"arabic":"أَكْمَلْتُ","translation":"আমি পূর্ণ করলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_044.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2689,"position":42,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_045.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2690,"position":43,"arabic":"دِينَكُمْ","translation":"দীনকে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_046.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2691,"position":44,"arabic":"وَأَتْمَمْتُ","translation":"ও আমি সম্পূর্ণ করলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_047.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2692,"position":45,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_048.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2693,"position":46,"arabic":"نِعْمَتِى","translation":"আমার অনুগ্রহ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_049.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2694,"position":47,"arabic":"وَرَضِيتُ","translation":"ও আমি পছন্দ করলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/005_003_050.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2695,"position":48,"a